    "row": 126,
    "rowsha": "PFZZuS94H9+8UJz6KEpU2847QQMnOc/pvpG/DjeOCSQ=",
    "originContent": "post-render perturbation (alpha jitter, sub-pixel color noise, edge micro-dots,",
    "translatedContent": "희박한 고스트 픽셀)와 렌더러별 무작위화를 적용하여 같은 설정으로도"
  },
  {
    "row": 127,
    "rowsha": "1qMeq2kMkVpgsQlisDzcoQ9awyI66Tpba2qcOz3chXw=",
    "originContent": "sparse ghost pixels) and per-renderer randomization so that no two outputs are",
    "translatedContent": "두 출력이 픽셀 단위로 동일하지 않도록 합니다. 이는 AI"
  },
  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "3VTqYfQgY0berHcbAzK56A7NVgg6B4Snwx0QdXq2ee0=",
    "originContent": "pixel-identical — even with the same settings. This makes it impossible for AI",
